@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mokiuq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(v0))
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.63) * 0.79))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.89 + v0 + 0.91)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.55)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
